.DT
is_potion_or_salve
Disk World creator help
is_potion_or_salve

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_potion_or_salve -  This is the default function for checking if something can be sold in a potion shop.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_potion_or_salve(object ob)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - The object that someone is trying to sell to the shop
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
success 1 if the object can be sold, 0 if not
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/potion_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is the default function for checking if something can
be sold in a potion shop.  If you override this, there is no
reason to inherit this file, so you can't.  It will accept any
object that contains something which has an eat effect or an
apply effect.
.EP

